text: Valle Cannobina is a comune in the Province of Verbano-Cusio-Ossola in the Italian region of Piedmont. It was created on 1 January 2019 from the former municipalities of Cavaglio-Spoccia, Cursolo-Orasso and Falmenta. Category:2019 establishments in Italy Category:Settlements in Verbano-Cusio-Ossola
